    "---\n",
    "## 2. Survey Response Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Each employee rated their manager on all 8 Oxygen behaviors using a 1 to 5 scale (1 = strongly disagree, 5 = strongly agree). We start by looking at the distribution of ratings across the full dataset to understand where managers tend to be strong and where gaps exist.\n"
